data.description: BACK ON MARKET DUE TO BUYER FINANCING. This adorable Lakeshore Bungalow is move in ready! It has just been freshly painted inside and out and is ready for you to make it your own! Enjoy relaxing on your front porch swing with a cup of coffee or glass of wine. You will love the remodeled Kitchen that has been opened to the dining and living areas. The Kitchen features white cabinets, quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and a farmhouse sink! The living room features a beautiful electric fireplace with stone accent and wood mantle. Wood floors have just been refinished. You will love that this home has two full baths and indoor laundry! Home sits on a beautiful lot, with a fully fenced backyard. The shed in the back has power to it and also has a window AC  unit. NEW AC 2020.
